x4freetext: From graphic bars (statistical) and
digitizing error
In the text (p.534) the authors gave the value
(2.49+-0.37)mb/sr for the cross section of the
7Li(He3,alpha0)6Li reaction at 160 degr.lab. and 6 MeV
bombarding energy. But on the figure the value of the
appropriated cross section equal 3.0 mb/sr.
